{"title":"奔腾——观一幅摄影有感","authors":["王恩宇"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":5,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——观一幅摄影有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王恩宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可听到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种强劲的呼啸？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可感到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种激烈的震动？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这骏马奋蹄的雄姿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以其特殊的风采，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特殊的魅力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总让人们的心失去应有的平衡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐于负重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望奔腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不与懒散者为伍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志在征途遥遥、关山重重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首驰骋千万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显示着非凡的坚毅和韧性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋进的雄心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作飞驰的闪电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"执著的追求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇入坚实的蹄声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切怠惰和懦弱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会在这身影和蹄声中颤栗、消遁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这矫健不屈的形象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂昂然，留在天地间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留在人们的钟爱和钦佩中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是力的凝聚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是勇的象征，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就凭这副神态这般气势，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不相信：一路上任何坎坷和荆棘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都能被它跨越、被它战胜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于它的词汇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有徘徊，没有退却，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远以充沛的精力宣示着——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳作终生，奔驰毕生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然有一天疲累得倒下了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也把奋力腾跃的志气写满征程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可听到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种激越的嘶鸣？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可感到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种心灵的震动？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！骏马奔腾图以鲜明的启迪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让人情思飞翔、热血奔涌……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}